OL,3,CSugar tax changes: The drinks that
OL,4,Ccould be affected by the new levy
OL,6,FBritons favourite drinks including
OL,7,FFanta, Pepsi and Yazoo could soon face
OL,8,Fa sugar tax. ITV News Reporter
OL,9,FSangeeta Kandola explains
OL,11,FThe sugar tax applied to fizzy drinks
OL,12,Fis set to be extended to milkshakes
OL,13,Fand similar treats under Government
OL,14,Fproposals.
OL,16,FPlans to end the sugar tax exemption
OL,17,Ffor dairy and non-dairy drinks like
OL,18,Foat or rice milk were put out for
OL,19,Fconsultation on Monday.
