OL,4,Ccould be affected by the new levy
OL,6,FAccording to Government analysis,
OL,7,Faround 203 pre-packed milk-based
OL,8,Fdrinks - accounting for 93% of sales
OL,9,Fin the category - will face the sugar
OL,10,Ftax unless their sugar content is cut
OL,11,Funder the new proposals.
OL,13,FThe Treasury said young people only
OL,14,Fget 3.5% of their calcium intake from
OL,15,Fdairy drinks, meaning "it is also
OL,16,Flikely that the health benefits do not
OL,17,Fjustify the harms from excess sugar".
