OL,15,FWhat exactly is the sugar tax?
OL,17,FThe sugar tax, officially called the
OL,18,FSoft Drinks Industry Levy (SDIL), is a
OL,19,Fcharge on pre-packaged drinks such as
OL,20,Fthose sold in cans and cartons in
OL,21,Fsupermarkets.
