OL,6,FIntroduced by the Conservatives in
OL,7,F2018 to help tackle obesity, it
OL,8,Fapplies to manufacturers.
OL,10,FWhat is classed as sugar in law?
OL,12,FThe sugar tax applies to drinks
OL,13,Fcontaining added sugars such as
OL,14,Fsucrose, glucose, fructose, lactose
OL,15,Fand galactose.
OL,17,FIt does not apply to drinks sweetened
OL,18,Fwith sugar replacements like stevia,
OL,19,Faspartame or sucralose.
