OL,6,FThe sugar tax is charged in two bands
OL,7,Fand was updated in the Autumn 2024
OL,8,FBudget:
OL,10,FWho pays the levy?
OL,12,FFor drinks packaged in the UK, the
OL,13,Fcompany that bottles or cans them is
OL,14,Fresponsible for paying the sugar tax.
OL,16,FIf manufacturers don't cut the sugar
OL,17,Fcontent, they're likely to pass the
OL,18,Fcost on to shoppers through higher
OL,19,Fprices.
